title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Other Insurance for Euro area (17 countries) (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category "Other Insurance (12.5.5)" is a classification of durable goods and services that includes service charges for other insurance such as civil liability for injury or damage to third parties or their property.

This category excludes civil liability or damage to third parties or their property arising from the operation of personal transport equipment (12.5.4).

This category is a subcategory of the Miscellaneous Goods and Service (12) and of Insurance (12.5).

Information provided in the notes pertaining to HICP classifications can be found from the source at: http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cache/metadata/en/prc_hicp_esms.htm.
